                  is the most commonly studied species. Within this topic, research does not tend to be focused more on threatened species.\n                  \n                \n                \n                  The effects of water pollution and eutrophication on bats remain unclear: different effects are reported for different species and in different areas.\n                \n                \n                  \n                    More studies are needed from\n                    A\n                    frica,\n                    S\n                    outh\n                    A\n                    merica, and Asia, regions for which few data are available, as well as from arid regions where fresh water is a limited resource.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Salvarina, Ioanna", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/080897467116afba2e01194420f21b5e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/d0ad531427399f7e7121a37e594fe1325c87fcdac3eb3769091d9a4bc8c226d8", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/XI85IDHC", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/XI85IDHC", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/1f6fdcf5b6f060922540ed280a3167c1!/b160148-162596", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "s